data.description: If you are looking for a spacious, charming home, look no further!!! This perfectly maintained home has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms with a transferable Home Warranty until January 2028.  The living area features 13' beamed ceilings with floor-to-ceiling windows and plantation shutters. 100% ceramic tile throughout the home. Large kitchen with oversized functional island that accommodates breakfast seating for 4 and is perfect for entertaining.  Quartz countertops, walk-in pantry, reverse osmosis system, and backsplash.  An abundance of tall beautiful slow-closed cabinets lines the kitchen walls.  The kitchen features a beautiful eat-in area perfect for casual dining.  For a more formal setting check out the formal dining area.  This home also boasts a huge master bedroom with a master bath including double vanities, a separate whirlpool garden bathtub, and an extended-size glass shower with a rain shower head.  The master suite is topped off with a large walk-in closet.  Discover the guest suite with a large walk-in closet and private full bathroom.  This room also includes a large newly built-in linen closet. The secondary bedroom is spacious and has a walk-in closet. An additional bedroom features a built-in queen-size Murphy bed (which will remain with the home). This room also contains a built-in office area with an ergonomic desktop.  Inside laundry room with vent. The list of amenities goes on and on!!  A sprinkler system, water softener, alarm system, and remote garage door opener round out the luxuries of the home. This listing is in a great location! Easy access to I-90, 1604, Lackland, SeaWorld and plenty of shopping and restaurants galore!
